<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA22" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>aṟiyu mulakellām yāṉēyu mallēṉ</l>
<l>poṟikoḷ ciṟaiyuvaṇa mūrntāy – veṟikamaḻuṅ</l>
<l>kāmpēymeṉ ṟōḷi kaṭaiveṇṇe yuṇṭāyait</l>
<l>tāmpēkoṇ ṭārtta taḻumpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All the world knows, not only me,</l>
<l>o you who mounted Suparṇa with spotted wings,</l>
<l>– about the scars [obtained] when [she with] bamboo-like soft shoulders scented</l>
<l>with perfume tied you, who had eaten the churned butter, with a rope.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
